#: src/TodoPage.qml:341
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Welcome introduction text"
msgid ""
"<p>KomoDo is a To-Do list application that uses <a href='https://github.com/"
"todotxt/todo.txt'>todo.txt</a> rules.</p><p>The rules are fairly quick to "
"learn and KomoDo has help sections for it: <br>On the toolbar, click the "
"<i><interface>Help…</interface></i> button.<br>While editing a task, click "
"the <i><interface>Syntax Information…</interface></i> button.</p><p>You can "
"follow the rules as much or as little as you wish.<br> Feel free to "
"experiment to find out your ideal way of managing tasks.</p><p>Click "
"<i><interface>Open To-Do list…</interface></i> to use an existing list or "
"<i><interface>Create New To-Do list…</interface></i> to start a new list.</p>"
msgstr ""
"<p>KomoDo je aplikacija za seznam opravil, ki uporablja pravila <a "
"href='https://github.com/todotxt/todo.txt'>todo.txt</a>.</p><p>Pravila se da "
"dokaj hitro naučiti in KomoDo ima zanje razdelke s pomočjo: <br>V orodni "
"vrstici kliknite gumb <i><interface>Pomoč…</interface></i>.<br>Med urejanjem "
"opravila kliknite gumb <i><interface>Informacije o skladnji…</interface></i>."
"</p><p>Pravila lahko upoštevate, kolikor malo želite.<br> Prosto "
"eksperimentirajte in odkrijte svoj idealen način upravljanja opravil.</"
"p><p>Kliknite <i><interface>Odpri seznam opravil…</interface></i>, če želite "
"uporabiti obstoječi seznam, ali <i><interface>Ustvari nov seznam opravil…</"
"interface></i>, če želite začeti nov seznam.</p>"

